com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Mainline.Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Mainline.Key
  • Enclosing class:
    Mainline

    public static class Mainline.Key
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a mainline key in a Spriter SCML file. A mainline key holds an id, a time, a curve and lists of bone and object references which build a tree hierarchy.
